short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Help you to easily try the newest and most popular StableDiffusion models in CivitAI, and create your own artwork on TryYourAI.com.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension provides image generation service for CivitAI. To get started, install this extension and open CivitAI. With just a simple click on the “TRY” button, you can use the most popular StableDiffusion models to create your own artworks on TryYourAI.com.
